  "instructions": [
    "Combine water, caraway seeds, coriander powder, salt, sugar, and apple cider vinegar in a saucepan and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes, then remove from heat.",
    "In a separate pan, heat coconut oil over medium heat.",
    "Add silken tofu and cook until lightly browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Transfer tofu to a serving dish and pour the fermented brine over it.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot.",
    "Optional: Sprinkle with black pepper to taste."
